rpc.model
Class RelationalPC

java.lang.Object
  rpc.model.RelationalPC

public class RelationalPC
extends java.lang.Object

The Relational PC algorithm for learning partially directed causal models of relational domains. RPC consists of two separate phases: skeleton identification and edge orientation. It is a relational extension to the PC algorithm (Spirtes, Glymour, & Scheines 2001).

setSignficanceThresholdAdjust

public void setSignficanceThresholdAdjust(double alpha)
Set the base alpha significance level threshold used for statistical tests. This threshold will be adjusted using the Bonferonni correction based on the total number of possible dependencies used in Phase I.

Parameters:
alpha - base significance threshold.
